CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Strongly Reciprocal

This project is licensed under the CERN OHL v2-SR.

You may copy, modify, and distribute the design files, provided that:
- You include this license in any redistribution,
- You document changes clearly,
- You make the modified source files available under the same license.

This license is intended to promote sharing and improvement of hardware designs while ensuring that all derivative works remain free and open.

---

Additional Ethical Restriction (Non-Military Use)

In addition to the terms of the CERN OHL v2-SR:

**The use of this project, in whole or in part, for any military, violent, or state-sponsored armed purpose is strictly prohibited.**

This includes, but is not limited to:
- Use in the design, manufacturing, or operation of real-world weapons
- Use in armed conflict, military R&D, or government combat programs
- Integration into military equipment or platforms

Anyone found violating this clause automatically loses the right to use, modify, or distribute this project.

